title: EP 29: Full Interview with Tyler Ward from BarnBridge [BONUS]
description:
You've listened to the episode on BarnBridge, how it works and suggestions to  be made.    

Here's the full interview with Tyler Ward, as he explains what they are doing,  what they can do in the future and how the tokens in Barnbridge works.    Enjoy!

The summary version with the product economics is the previous episode before this.
